f = op.models.physics.capillary_pressure.washburn
self.phys.add_model(propname='pore.capillary_pressure', model=f,
    surface_tension='pore.surface_tension', contact_angle=
    'pore.contact_angle', diameter='pore.diameter')
self.phys.add_model(propname='throat.capillary_pressure', model=f,
    surface_tension='pore.surface_tension', contact_angle=
    'pore.contact_angle', diameter='throat.diameter')
self.phys.regenerate_models()
a = 0.14399999999999993
assert_approx_equal(self.water['pore.capillary_pressure'][0], a)
self.phys.remove_model('pore.capillary_pressure')
